.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-live/israel-braces-for-general-strike-after-night-of-protests-in-support-of-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b077-d25b-aff7-f4f7214f0005</link><description>数十万人走上街头抗议数小时后，以色列各地开始大罢工 ■ 特拉维夫抗议后，25 人仍被拘留 ■ 奥斯汀对加兰特：哈马斯领导人必须承担责任 ■ 白宫表示，拜登、哈里斯将与谈判团队会面 ■逾千人参加纽约市为哈马斯杀害六名人质举行的守夜活动</description><pubDate>Mon, 02 Sep 2024 03:04:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-02/ty-article-live/israel-braces-for-general-strike-after-night-of-protests-in-support-of-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b077-d25b-aff7-f4f7214f0005</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：尽管人质被谋杀，以色列不会在加沙费城路线上妥协</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-will-not-compromise-on-gazas-philadelphi-route-despite-hostage-murders/00000191-aeff-d875-a3bb-aeff6bc20000</link><description>在安全内阁决定以色列不应从埃及-加沙边境撤军后，官员们正在努力预测在哈马斯囚禁的六名人质被谋杀后停火谈判将如何发展</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 20:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-israel-will-not-compromise-on-gazas-philadelphi-route-despite-hostage-murders/00000191-aeff-d875-a3bb-aeff6bc20000</guid></item><item><title>人质的父亲：“这是一场活生生的噩梦。”如果内塔尼亚胡不完成这件事，就会有更多的尸体”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-09-01/ty-article-podcast/hostages-father-if-netanyahu-doesnt-get-this-done-there-will-be-more-bodies/00000191-ae14-d67c-a3bd-efd72cac0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 19:43:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-09-01/ty-article-podcast/hostages-father-if-netanyahu-doesnt-get-this-done-there-will-be-more-bodies/00000191-ae14-d67c-a3bd-efd72cac0000</guid></item><item><title>六名人质遇害后，以色列各地数十万人集会要求加沙达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/masses-rally-across-israel-demanding-gaza-deal-after-six-hostages-murdered/00000191-ae5b-d67c-a3bd-efdf0bec0000</link><description>“内塔尼亚胡每天都在玩俄罗斯轮盘赌，直到所有人质都死了”：以色列劳工联合会主席呼吁总罢工，数十万人走上街头，要求达成加沙人质协议</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 19:28:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/masses-rally-across-israel-demanding-gaza-deal-after-six-hostages-murdered/00000191-ae5b-d67c-a3bd-efdf0bec0000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团高级部长：内塔尼亚胡只会在“街道着火时”推动加沙协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-consults-staff-over-fears-of-mass-israeli-protests-demanding-gaza-cease-fire/00000191-ae85-dd1e-adb5-aecfd4dc0000</link><description>利库德集团一位高级部长表示，“承认这一点令人不快，但内塔尼亚胡只有在街道着火的情况下才会推动达成协议”，并补充道，“现在，他害怕本格维尔和斯莫特里奇，而不是人质家属”</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 18:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-consults-staff-over-fears-of-mass-israeli-protests-demanding-gaza-cease-fire/00000191-ae85-dd1e-adb5-aecfd4dc0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登，是时候说出有关以色列人质的痛苦真相了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-01/ty-article/.highlight/biden-its-time-to-tell-the-painful-truth-about-the-israeli-hostages/00000191-adfd-d67c-a3bd-efff5a5a0000</link><description>目前尚不清楚拜登政府是否能够在这种情况下真正达成协议。但如果做不到，它就欠人质家属一件事，尤其是美国人质家属：说实话，停止允许任何一方使用政治伎俩和操纵</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:22:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-01/ty-article/.highlight/biden-its-time-to-tell-the-painful-truth-about-the-israeli-hostages/00000191-adfd-d67c-a3bd-efff5a5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 331 天：部长表示，内塔尼亚胡拖延协议以拯救他的联盟</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-331-netanyahu-stalling-deal-to-save-his-coalition-says-minister/00000191-ae75-d875-a3bb-ae777bb00001</link><description>以色列国防军取回了 10 月 7 日被哈马斯扣押的六名人质的尸体，并补充说，他们最近在以色列军队到达他们之前被处决。 以色列劳工联合会主席周一宣布大罢工，称达成释放人质的协议“是比什么都重要” ■ 三名警察在约旦河西岸枪击事件中丧生 ■ 战争开始 331 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 17:03:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-331-netanyahu-stalling-deal-to-save-his-coalition-says-minister/00000191-ae75-d875-a3bb-ae777bb00001</guid></item><item><title>为了抗议内塔尼亚胡的残酷行为，以色列安全负责人是否应该辞职？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-protest-netanyahus-cruelty-should-israels-security-chiefs-resign/00000191-adc0-d95c-a5b5-ffd35e4a0000</link><description>以色列国防军、摩萨德和辛贝特的领导人面临着一个戏剧性的两难境地：他们是否继续为内塔尼亚胡领导的政府服务，而内塔尼亚胡是一个只致力于自己政治生存的破坏者，从而与人质的流血事件有牵连？</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 16:00:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article-opinion/.premium/to-protest-netanyahus-cruelty-should-israels-security-chiefs-resign/00000191-adc0-d95c-a5b5-ffd35e4a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列公众的关键时刻</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/the-israeli-publics-moment-of-truth/00000191-ae1f-d3dd-a991-ae1f75410000</link><description></description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 15:19:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/the-israeli-publics-moment-of-truth/00000191-ae1f-d3dd-a991-ae1f75410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列赛艇运动员莫兰·塞缪尔在 2024 年巴黎残奥会上获得金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-rower-moran-samuel-wins-gold-medal-at-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-adc5-d95c-a5b5-ffd799ec0000</link><description>这位42岁的赛艇运动员和前篮球运动员在资格赛中创造了新的残奥会纪录后，以10分25.4秒的成绩完成了2000米比赛，在整个比赛中保持了相当大的领先优势</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 15:00:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/israeli-rower-moran-samuel-wins-gold-medal-at-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-adc5-d95c-a5b5-ffd799ec0000</guid></item><item><title>逃离俄罗斯和乌克兰的青少年需要什么？这个以色列