-bank-seems-closer-than-ever/00000191-aceb-d4e9-a199-acef1aba0000</link><description>定居者在西岸对巴勒斯坦人不断实施的暴力行为，以及本格维尔在圣殿山的挑衅，可能会导致西岸发生暴力冲突</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:40:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/a-unity-of-fronts-between-gaza-and-west-bank-seems-closer-than-ever/00000191-aceb-d4e9-a199-acef1aba0000</guid></item><item><title>从加沙打捞出六名人质尸体后，以色列劳工联合会主席宣布大罢工</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/businesses-across-israel-to-close-early-ahead-of-mass-rally-for-hostage-deal/00000191-ad7a-d95c-a5b5-ff7bc4960000</link><description>由于全国大罢工，以色列国际机场将于周一上午 8 点开始暂停运营。餐馆、电影院和其他场所将在周日晚上提前关闭，以支持计划在特拉维夫举行的大规模集会</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:28:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/businesses-across-israel-to-close-early-ahead-of-mass-rally-for-hostage-deal/00000191-ad7a-d95c-a5b5-ff7bc4960000</guid></item><item><title>以色列北部的父母被迫在孩子的安全和教育之间做出选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/parents-in-northern-israel-forced-to-choose-between-childrens-safety-and-education/00000191-aa21-d2ec-a1f7-ef7178810000</link><description>在黎巴嫩近十一个月的持续轰炸中，政府未能找到解决受到威胁的道路和保护不足的教室的解决方案</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 12:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/parents-in-northern-israel-forced-to-choose-between-childrens-safety-and-education/00000191-aa21-d2ec-a1f7-ef7178810000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质死亡，内塔尼亚胡才能让他的联盟继续存在</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-finally-condemned-the-israeli-hostages-to-their-deaths-in-gaza/00000191-ad36-d4e9-a199-ad771b570000</link><description>出于政治考虑和军事压力而放弃被囚禁的以色列人，巩固了总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡作为独裁者的遗产，他显然对自己的公民没有任何责任感</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:56:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-01/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-has-finally-condemned-the-israeli-hostages-to-their-deaths-in-gaza/00000191-ad36-d4e9-a199-ad771b570000</guid></item></channel></rss>